  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Functional dyspepsia might have impaired gastric mucosal dysfunction and Puyuanhewei may be
      helpful to improve the symptoms of FD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study aimed to investigate the gastric mucosal dysfunction in functional dyspepsia (FD)
      and verify the efficacy of Puyuanhewei for treating FD and assess the relationship between
      gastric microalterations and therapeutic response by endomicroscopy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
